def insert_before_character(string):
    return string.replace('o', '0o')

print(insert_before_character('Hello world!'))  # Hell0o w0orld!
print(insert_before_character('Python is awesome!'))  # Pyth0on is awes0ome!
print(insert_before_character('This is a test'))  # This is a test
